!!!
%html{:lang => "ja"}
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
    %meta{:charset => "utf-8"}/
    %meta{:content => "IE=edge", "http-equiv" => "X-UA-Compatible"}/
    %meta{:content => "width=device-width, initial-scale=1", :name => "viewport"}/
    %meta{:content => "index page of willnet", :name => "description"}/
    %meta{:content => "Shinichi Maeshima", :name => "author"}/
    %title willnet.in
    %link{rel: 'shortcut icon', href: 'https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/willnet.in/favicon.ico'}
    %link{:href => "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/willnet.in/css/bootstrap.min.css", :rel => "stylesheet"}/
    %link{:href => "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/willnet.in/css/freelancer.css", :rel => "stylesheet"}/
    %link{:href => "//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.3.0/css/font-awesome.min.css", :rel => "stylesheet", :type => "text/css"}/
    %link{:href => "http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700", :rel => "stylesheet", :type => "text/css"}/
    %link{:href => "http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:400,700,400italic,700italic", :rel => "stylesheet", :type => "text/css"}/
    / HTML5 Shim and Respond.js IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries
    / WARNING: Respond.js doesn't work if you view the page via file://
    /[if lt IE 9]
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/html5shiv/3.7.0/html5shiv.js"></script>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/respond.js/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
  %body#page-top.index
    / Navigation
    %nav.navbar.navbar-default.navbar-fixed-top
      .container
        / Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display
        .navbar-header.page-scroll
          %button.navbar-toggle{"data-target" => "#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :type => "button"}
            %span.sr-only Toggle navigation
            %span.icon-bar
            %span.icon-bar
            %span.icon-bar
          %a.navbar-brand{:href => "#page-top"} willnet.in
        / Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling
        #bs-example-navbar-collapse-1.collapse.navbar-collapse
          %ul.nav.navbar-nav.navbar-right
            %li.hidden
              %a{:href => "#page-top"}
            %li.page-scroll
              %a{:href => "#portfolio"} Portfolio
            %li.page-scroll
              %a{:href => "#about"} About
        / /.navbar-collapse
      / /.container-fluid
    / Header
    %header
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12
            %img.img-responsive{:width => 250, :height => 250, :alt => "", :src => "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/willnet.in/img/profile.png"}/
            .intro-text
              %span.name Shinichi Maeshima
              %hr.star-light/
              %span.skills Freelance Rails Engineer
    / Portfolio Grid Section
    %section#portfolio
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12.text-center
            %h2 Portfolio
            %hr.star-primary/
        .row
          .col-sm-4.portfolio-item
            %a.portfolio-link{"data-toggle" => "modal", :href => "#portfolioModal1"}
              .caption
                .caption-content
                  %i.fa.fa-search-plus.fa-3x
              %img.img-responsive{:alt => "", :src => "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/willnet.in/img/portfolio/savanna.png"}/
          .col-sm-4.portfolio-item
            %a.portfolio-link{"data-toggle" => "modal", :href => "#portfolioModal2"}
              .caption
                .caption-content
                  %i.fa.fa-search-plus.fa-3x
              %img.img-responsive{:alt => "", :src => "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/willnet.in/img/portfolio/revenger.png"}/
          .col-sm-4.portfolio-item
            %a.portfolio-link{"data-toggle" => "modal", :href => "#portfolioModal3"}
              .caption
                .caption-content
                  %i.fa.fa-search-plus.fa-3x
              %img.img-responsive{:alt => "", :src => "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/willnet.in/img/portfolio/miuchee.png"}/
    / About Section
    %section#about.success
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12.text-center
            %h2 About
            %hr.star-light/
        .row
          .col-lg-4.col-lg-offset-2
            %p 前島真一。東京在住。ネット上では willnet もしくは netwillnet として活動しています。(“willnet” は時々他の人に取られています…) 現在はフリーランスwebエンジニアをしています。
          .col-lg-4
            %p 得意なのは Rails を使ったサーバサイドプログラミングです。<a href="http://gihyo.jp/book/2014/978-4-7741-6516-5">パーフェクトRuby on Rails</a> の著者。<a href="http://ginzarb.github.io/">ginza.rb<a/>、<a href="http://yurufuwa.club/">ゆるデ部</a>、<a href="https://debeg.doorkeeper.jp/">デザインビギナーズ</a>の主催をしています。
    / Footer
    %footer.text-center
      .footer-above
        .container
          .row
            .footer-col.col-md-6
              %h3 Blog
              %ul.list-inline
                %li
                  %a.btn-social.btn-outline{:href => "http://blog.willnet.in/"}
                    %i.fa.fa-fw.fa-diamond
                %li
                  %a.btn-social.btn-outline{:href => "http://memo.willnet.in/"}
                    %i.fa.fa-fw.fa-pencil
                %li
                  %a.btn-social.btn-outline{:href => "http://private.willnet.in/"}
                    %i.fa.fa-fw.fa-home
            .footer-col.col-md-6
              %h3 Around the Web
              %ul.list-inline
                %li
                  %a.btn-social.btn-outline{:href => "https://github.com/willnet"}
                    %i.fa.fa-fw.fa-github
                %li
                  %a.btn-social.btn-outline{:href => "https://twitter.com/netwillnet"}
                    %i.fa.fa-fw.fa-twitter
                %li
                  %a.btn-social.btn-outline{:href => "https://www.facebook.com/netwillnet"}
                    %i.fa.fa-fw.fa-facebook
                %li
                  %a.btn-social.btn-outline{:href => "https://plus.google.com/110960561695652777519?rel=author"}
                    %i.fa.fa-fw.fa-google-plus
                %li
                  %a.btn-social.btn-outline{:href => "https://jp.linkedin.com/in/maeshima"}
                    %i.fa.fa-fw.fa-linkedin
      .footer-below
        .container
          .row
            .col-lg-12
              Copyright © willnet.in 2015
    / Scroll to Top Button (Only visible on small and extra-small screen sizes)
    .scroll-top.page-scroll.visible-xs.visible-sm
      %a.btn.btn-primary{:href => "#page-top"}
        %i.fa.fa-chevron-up
    / Portfolio Modals
    #portfolioModal1.portfolio-modal.modal.fade{"aria-hidden" => "true", :role => "dialog", :tabindex => "-1"}
      .modal-content
        .close-modal{"data-dismiss" => "modal"}
          .lr
            .rl
        .container
          .row
            .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
              .modal-body
                %h2
                  %a{href: 'https://savanna.io'}
                    savanna
                %hr.star-primary/
                %a{href: 'https://savanna.io'}
                  %img.img-responsive.img-centered{:alt => "", :src => "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/willnet.in/img/portfolio/savanna.png"}/
                %p フリーランスのWebエンジニア、Webデザイナー向けのコミュニティサイトです
                %button.btn.btn-default{"data-dismiss" => "modal", :type => "button"}
                  %i.fa.fa-times
                  Close
    #portfolioModal2.portfolio-modal.modal.fade{"aria-hidden" => "true", :role => "dialog", :tabindex => "-1"}
      .modal-content
        .close-modal{"data-dismiss" => "modal"}
          .lr
            .rl
        .container
          .row
            .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
              .modal-body
                %h2
                  %a{:href => "https://revenger.in"}
                    revenger
                %hr.star-primary/
                %a{:href => "https://revenger.in"}
                  %img.img-responsive.img-centered{:alt => "", :src => "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/willnet.in/img/portfolio/revenger.png"}/
                %p 一度学んだことを定着させるための復習メモサービスです
                %button.btn.btn-default{"data-dismiss" => "modal", :type => "button"}
                  %i.fa.fa-times
                  Close
    #portfolioModal3.portfolio-modal.modal.fade{"aria-hidden" => "true", :role => "dialog", :tabindex => "-1"}
      .modal-content
        .close-modal{"data-dismiss" => "modal"}
          .lr
            .rl
        .container
          .row
            .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
              .modal-body
                %h2
                  %a{:href => "http://miuchee.jp"}
                    micuhee
                %hr.star-primary/
                %a{:href => "http://miuchee.jp"}
                  %img.img-responsive.img-centered{:alt => "", :src => "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/willnet.in/img/portfolio/miuchee.png"}/
                %p
                  Twitter を利用して、お手軽に親孝行するためのサービスです
                %button.btn.btn-default{"data-dismiss" => "modal", :type => "button"}
                  %i.fa.fa-times
                  Close
